                     <interp inst="t17870418-2-off6" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17870418-2-cd7" type="crimeDate">9th day of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17870418-2-off6 t17870418-2-cd7"></join>, thirty yards of printed linen, value 30 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17870418-2-victim58" type="victimName">
                           James 
                           Gibson
                        <interp inst="t17870418-2-victim58" type="surname" value="Gibson"></interp>
