                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17870418-2-defend55 t17870418-2-punish11"></join>
               Death
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>She was humbly recommended to mercy by the Jury and Prosecutor.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. 
